@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ltkqpk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (((v1 + 0.36 + v2 + 0.29) - wp.exp(tmp + 0.88)) / 0.37)
    v2 = 0.97
    v0 = 0.70
    v0 = (tmp * tmp)
    v0 = v1
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.exp(wp.abs(v2 + 0.40)))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.cos(wp.abs(v1 + 0.49)))
    data[tid] = v0
